        "        <div style=\"font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.55\">At <strong id=\"ci-rule-rate\" style=\"color:var(--ink)\">10%</strong>, your money doubles every <strong id=\"ci-rule-yrs\" style=\"color:var(--orange)\">7.2 years</strong>. Start at 20, not 30 - that is 2.6x more by retirement.</div>\n",
        "      </div>\n",
        "    </div>\n",
        "  </div>\n",
        "\n",
