        "        </div>\n",
        "      </div>\n",
        "      <div style=\"font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5\">This is why keeping all savings in cash loses you money. The Fed targets ~2% inflation. When they raise interest rates, borrowing gets expensive - mortgages, car loans, credit cards all cost more.</div>\n",
